This document will serve to track changes and installs made to the bluefeeds server to assist in future migration of the environment to other machines.

The basic install is as follows:

Current versions of a basic LAMP install:

-mySql
-php5
-apache2

Administrative tools:

-phpmyadmin

Supplementary software:

-imagemagick (for image processing)

The following configuration changes were made:

in /etc/php5/apache2/php.ini the max_upload_filesize and post_max_size were raised to accomodate large image files